// DiagramEditor
// Full split-pane editor for Mermaid diagrams.
// Combines a CodeMirrorWrapper (left) with a live MermaidPreview (right).
// For SMACH YAML diagrams, adds a SmachPropertiesPane for state/transition
// editing. Provides rich node/edge editing via context menus and a
// CreateNodeDialog.

isSmachContent determines whether the diagram is a SMACH state machine.
Edit mode drives whether node/edge clicks trigger selection vs context menu.
Selection modes (add-transition, change-origin, change-destination) are
transient overlays on top of normal navigation.

FUNCTION DiagramEditor(diagram, onContentChange, onSave, ...) -> JSX   EXPORT
  CALLS: CodeMirrorWrapper (CodeMirrorWrapper), MermaidPreview (MermaidPreview),
         SmachPropertiesPane (SmachPropertiesPane), isSmachContent (SmachPropertiesPane)
  Renders a SplitPane with code editor on the left and preview on the right.
  Optionally renders SmachPropertiesPane for SMACH diagrams.
  Overlays NodeContextMenu / EdgeContextMenu when a node/edge is right-clicked.
  Shows CreateNodeDialog when user initiates node creation.
  Keyboard shortcut Ctrl+S triggers save.

---

FUNCTION handleChangeEdgeEndpoint(nodeId) -> void
  Rewrites the edge in the diagram content using regex to change either
  the origin or destination node ID, depending on current selection mode.

---

FUNCTION handleNodeClick(nodeId, position) -> void
  In add-transition mode: starts the transition with nodeId as origin.
  In change-origin/change-destination mode: calls handleChangeEdgeEndpoint.
  Otherwise: shows NodeContextMenu at position.

---

FUNCTION handleEdgeClick(edgeId, position) -> void
  Extracts the edge label from the diagram content.
  Shows EdgeContextMenu at position with the label.

---

FUNCTION handleCreateNode(nodeId, label, nodeType) -> void
  Calls generateNodeId, buildNodeDefinition, buildNodeStyle,
  findNodeInsertionPoint to produce the new lines. Inserts them into content.

---

FUNCTION handleEditNodeLabel(nodeId, newLabel) -> void
  Uses regex to replace the node's label in the content lines.

---

FUNCTION handleChangeNodeType(nodeId, newType) -> void
  Updates the shape brackets and style class for the node in content.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteNode(nodeId) -> void
  Finds the node line, all edges referencing it, and its style line.
  Removes all found lines from content via removeLines.

---

FUNCTION handleEditEdgeLabel(edgeId, newLabel) -> void
  Uses regex with optional label capture group to rewrite the edge label.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteEdge(edgeId) -> void
  Finds the edge line and removes it.

---

FUNCTION handleStartAddTransition() -> void
  Enters add-transition selection mode (next node click sets origin).

---

FUNCTION handleStartChangeOrigin(edgeId) -> void
  Enters change-origin mode for the given edge.

---

FUNCTION handleStartChangeDestination(edgeId) -> void
  Enters change-destination mode for the given edge.

---

FUNCTION handleSmachEditDescription(stateName, description) -> void
  Updates the description field in the YAML content for the named state.

---

FUNCTION handleSmachEditTransition(stateName, transitionIndex, newTransition) -> void
  Stub — updates a SMACH transition in YAML content.

---

FUNCTION handleSmachAddTransition(stateName) -> void
  Stub — adds a new SMACH transition in YAML content.

---

FUNCTION handleSmachRemoveTransition(stateName, transitionIndex) -> void
  Stub — removes a SMACH transition from YAML content.
